oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: 1,4-bis(3-quinolyl)-1,3-butadiyne
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The S atom in the thiophene ring is disordered between positions 1 and 3. The molecular packing would not afford any facile mechanism for crystal-phase polymerization. The thiophene ring is rotated by 55-degrees with respect to the plane of the quinoline system.
